  <dinner><![CDATA[<p>For those guests who choose the half board basis then you can dine in the beautiful N<strong>axos Restaurant</strong> that overlooks the Gulf of Naxos. There is a daily set menu or you can choose à la carte menu that offers traditional Sicilian cuisine and International cuisine. </p>]]></dinner>
