  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Atahotel Capotaormina overlooks the Giardini Naxos Bay and is surrounded by a gorgeous landscape, located about 2.5km below Taormina. With its own private beach, salt water pool and wellness centre you'll be spoiled for choice when it comes to finding the perfect spot to relax. The staff here couldn't be more welcoming - experience the true Sicilian hospitality for yourself. </p>]]></listingDescription>
